Description: PyFuzzyBool
        ======
        
        Additional boolean values: KindaTrue, KindaFalse, VeryTrue, and VeryFalse. (This is a joke project.)
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        To install with pip, run:
        
            pip install pyfuzzybool
        
        Quickstart Guide
        ----------------
        
            >>> from pyfuzzybool import *
            >>> KindaTrue == KindaFalse
            True
            >>> KindaTrue == True
            False
            >>> VeryTrue == True
            True
            >>> VeryFalse == False
            True
            >>> KindaFalse == False
            False
            >>> fuzzybool(1)
            fuzzybool(True)
            >>> fuzzybool(0.9)
            KindaTrue
            >>> fuzzybool(0)
            fuzzybool(False)
            >>> fuzzybool(-1)
            VeryFalse
            >>> fuzzybool(1.1)
            VeryTrue
            >>> fuzzybool()
            KindaFalse
            >>> KindaFalse < True
            True
            >>> KindaFalse > False
            True
            >>> KindaFalse <= KindaTrue
            True
        
        Contribute
        ----------
        
        If you'd like to contribute to PyFuzzyBool, check out https://github.com/asweigart/pyfuzzybool
        
